A prominent industrial location occupied by a variety of users of both a local and regional nature. Centrally located providing excellent access to M4, M7 and the M5 Motorways.

- 2,000sqm* Building Area
- Internal clearance of up to 12m*
- Two (2) overhead gantry cranes
- Accessible via four (4) container height roller doors
- Exclusive yard area for truck manoeuvrability
- Bathroom amenities available 
- Ample parking available
- Fully sprinklered facility 
- Zoned IN1 General Industrial 
- Available with 1 months' notice

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact either of the exclusive agents listed.

*approx

CBRE is pleased to offer Building 2i, Yennora Distribution Centre for lease.

Features Include:
- B-Double approved transport facility
- Accessed provided by three (3) roller shutter doors
- Container loading/unloading area
- Short and long term opportunities available
- On-site café
- 6km from the M4*

Please contact the exclusive agents Janet Joljian or Michael O'Neill for further information.

CBRE and LJ Hooker are pleased to offer 3 Antill St, Yennora to the market for lease. Centrally located with direct access to Railway Street and Woodville Road.

- Building Area: 1,383sqm
- High clearance clear span warehouse with clearance up to 7.5m* 
- Dual access via The Prominade & Antill Street
- 200 Amps power supply. 
- Mezzanine office area of featuring a boardroom, lunchroom & partitioned offices. 
- Zoned IN2 light industrial.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact either of the exclusive agents listed.

*approx
